column_description: Unique identifier for each dog in the kennel
Identifier linking the dog to its owner in the 'Owners' table
Indicates whether the dog has been abandoned (1 for yes, 0 for no)
Code representing the breed of the dog, linked to the 'Breeds' table
Code representing the size of the dog, linked to the 'Sizes' table
The age of the dog, stored as a string
The date and time of the dog's birth
The gender of the dog (1 for male, 0 for female)
The weight of the dog, stored as a string
The date and time when the dog arrived at the kennel
The date and time when the dog was adopted
The date and time when the dog left the kennel
